  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Individuals operated for rhegmatogenous retinal detachment will be prospectively evaluated
      for postoperative retinal shift. Fundus autofluorescence will be used to evaluate retinal
      shift that will be correlated to visual acuity, metamorphopsia, aniseikonia, and stereopsis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
